cs.NE, cs.ET, cs.AR, cs.EM, cs.CE 

This paper is about spiking neural networks (SNNs) and their implementation using resistive RAM (RRAM) arrays. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Other likely categories include cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), cs.AR (Hardware Architecture), cs.EM (Electromagnetics), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering).
